author: Scott
title: Scott
text: This place needs better cleaning service and maintance service. Cabin was not clean had a small bug problem plus every other thing is broke or very dirty. Really needs work on this cabin if they expect to get top dollar for this place. Not to mention how close everyone is together in this community needs less cabins an better services to get top pay for these places. Rented with this company before an the cabin was top notched clean not to close an well maintained was worth every penny spent on it however this time not worth it.
